data.description: Massive $94K reduction in price! Seller is moving and needs close quickly. This is a Premium home on a Premium lot. If you build this same home with the same upgrades if would cost around $800k with the builder. This dream home is located in the highly coveted area of Haslet! It's a stunning 5-bed, 4-bath, 3-car garage property that sits on a Lot over a quarter of an acre. It features an open-concept living area and a gourmet kitchen with granite countertops and a 5-burner gas cooktop with a custom wood vent. Imagine family dinners, entertaining friends and relaxing. The primary bedroom is spacious featuring a luxurious ensuite bathroom with walk-in closet. The oversized game room is perfect for Fun nights or a second living room hang out spot, while the media room 7.1 surround sound, will feel like you are in the cinema. The owners spent over $150k upgrading this home, custom double 8' Wood entry doors, widening the house, raising the living room ceiling, and more. Don't wait!
